Date: Fri, 20 Apr 2018 08:41:48 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 6/8] dts: add new espressobin dts for hw rev.7

Since ESPRESSObin hw rev.7 changed the ethernet port definition,
so we need to change the ethernet port mapping.

the port mapping on the board : |USB2|WAN|LAN0|LAN1|USB3|
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/Makefile               |  1 +
 .../boot/dts/marvell/armada-3720-community-v7.dts  | 65 ++++++++++++++++++++++
 2 files changed, 66 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/armada-3720-community-v7.dts

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/Makefile b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/Makefile
index 9543788..7112995 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/Makefile
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/Makefile
@@ -8,6 +8,7 @@ dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_MVEBU) += armada-3720-db-B.dtb
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_MVEBU) += armada-3720-db-C.dtb
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_MVEBU) += armada-3720-community.dtb
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_MVEBU) += armada-3720-community-v5.dtb
+dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_MVEBU) += armada-3720-community-v7.dtb
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_MVEBU) += armada-37x0-customer.dtb
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_MVEBU) += armada-3900-db-axis.dtb
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_MVEBU) += armada-3900-db-vd.dtb
diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/armada-3720-community-v7.dts b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/armada-3720-community-v7.dts
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..f79055c
--- /dev/null
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/armada-3720-community-v7.dts
@@ -0,0 +1,65 @@
